_header: As solemn as stately as strange toward me
_description: Song of lover’s complaint — three-line fragment

NYPLDrexFr4185.Transcription:
…As solen as staytly as strange toward meas I of [ ] had neuer
                    bene aforeWher fore I…
NYPLDrexFr4185.Note:
Portions of pages cut away to fit as endleaves to seventeenth-century
                    song book.
